-- Ukraine to Auction Kharkivska Power Plant, Kommersant Reports
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-10-18T06:41:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-18/ukraine-to-auction-kharkivska-power-plant-kommersant-reports.html
Ukraine is to auction a 94.5 percent
stake in the Kharkivska Tets-5 heat and power plant on Nov. 7,
 Kommersant-Ukraine  reported, citing government documents.  The starting price for the holding is 279.5 million hryvnia
($34.3 million), according to Kiev-based Kommersant. Potential
bidders have to prove that they extract natural gas in Ukraine
and hold a license to use natural gas deposits with at least 1
billion cubic meters of the fuel, according to Kommersant.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  